name: Sneaky Beaky Level 1
description: You have the knowledge of stealing and sneaking away, your crouch walk speed is increased by 10% and you make less sounds while walking.

name: Medical License Level 1
description: With your medical knowledge you can heal other survivors 10% faster.

name: Thick Blood Level 1
description: You suffer from a rare condition that makes your blood very thick, the time for bloodpools to appear takes 15% longer.

name: Loose Fur Level 1
description: You can easily lose your fur while sprinting, this decreases the time of your fur to drop by 10% and your dropped fur is abit spread.

name: Believer Level 1
description: Your spirit is strong and you feel connected to the totems, vanish totems 3% faster.

name: BoxOGone Level 1
description: Dropped boxes fill you with rage and strength. You break boxes 20% faster.

name: Murder Hype Level 1
description: You are so hyped to kill a survivor that you gain a small endurance boost. Your lunge lasts 5% longer. Your cooldown for a attack is 5% longer.

name: Killer Train Level 1
description: Choo Choo here comes the killer! You move 1% faster and your monsterradius is increased by 15%.

description: Your weapon extended, your attack range is increased by 5%.

name: Stealth Killer Level 1
description: You learned to stay quiet and to surprise survivors. Decreases your monsterradius by 10%

name: Green Paw Level 1
description: You are one with nature and healing. You can be healed 5% faster and you heal others 5% faster.

name: Safety Helmet Level 1

name: Fluffy Boots Level 1

name: Rachel
description: Rachel, 19 years old, athlete, Rachel is a handsome and very fit cat. He is the leader of a athlete team, everyone in his team looks up to him but Rachel is never looking for friends, Rachel thinks making friends is easy but once you have a friend, its hard to let go. On the last tournament Rachel broke his leg and was send to a hospital. Rachels Team wanted to give him a visit after the tournament but he never arrived at the hospital. [Special Ability: Always number one, Gains a speed boost for 1 sec. Cooldown: 60 secs.]

name: Felix
description: Felix, 18 years old, school chess club, Felix is a very smart cat, he is the best in his class and learns to be the chess champion. Felix lives with his father after the passing of his mother. They don't have alot of money, thats why Felix needs to do sidejobs. Felix was last seen in school, he never arrived at home. [Special Ability: Killer Tracker App, Shows the location of the killer and all survivors for 10 secs. Cooldown: 50 secs.]

name: Sandy
description: Sandy, 24 years old, surgeon, Sandy is a experienced surgeon. Many cats are thankful to live for another day. Sandy saved many lives with her quick and efficient surgeries. After some years Sandy received an invite to work in a big facility called DCR, they need someone who knows alot about the cats anatomy. Its not clear if Sandy accepted the invite but she haven't returned to work after receiving the invite. [Special Ability: Self Surgery, Heal your own wounds if you are not downed.]

name: Led
description: Led, Scientists created two robots using one real brain, but one is programmed to be good and one to be bad. The experiment is done to see if the machines can develope real emotions by putting both in the same room for many years. It did not go well... [Special Ability: Two for One, switch between your red and blue version.]

name: Tinky
description: Tinky, 21 years old, electrician and game dev. [Special Ability: Improvised Bandage, after vanishing totems for 60 secs. this ability activates, after being downed Tinky gains the power to help himself up instantly.]

name: Racc (Prisoner Outfit)
description: Racc, 25 years old, No job, Racc lives under poor circumstances, he started his life of being a thief and steals from the rich,  after stealing a strange container from a research center, a cctv captured footage of Racc and the police went with a warrant to his house. The container was found but empty. Racc was never seen again. [Special Ability: Let me be clear, Becomes 20% transparent for 7 secs. Cooldown: 40 secs.]

description: Cinder, for others he was a freak, he is obsessed with spiders and always saw himself as one. He lost himself in the madness and got a offer he would never decline... [Special Ability: Sticky Web, places a web below himself that slows survivors by 30% and lasts for 20 secs. Cooldown: 5 secs.]

name: Vaz
description: Vaz, 31 years old, a experienced carpenter who makes out of old boring logs, perfect and beautiful furniture. He got his own shop where he sells his work and where he repairs other peoples broken furniture. [Special Ability: Reuse, Vanishing a totem for 30 secs activates this ability, using the ability lets you stack dropped boxes.]
